{"tid":1223513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好鐘意呢幾日既連登, 真香港人好可愛好團結","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T17:52:04.000Z","uid":47659,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8db81082036c326ec78bc142593c2986e06ce569","tid":1223513,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"星期五晚開下直線正能量post<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日既連登<br />\n無再自己攪分化, 無小圈子, 無代溝無人笑鳩90後00後<br />\n教眾被尊重唔會再比人笑<br />\n港女英勇表現令大家重新評價<br />\n台灣仔明白唇亡齒寒都支持我地 <br />\n<br />\n創意, 凝聚力, 全部放晒落去文宣同攻擊我地既敵人<br />\n笑話全部圍繞住黑警同正苦, 另類既抗爭方法<br />\n亦有好多post係展示戰亂之中人性既光輝<br />\n<br />\n雖然早幾日大家會過得好辛苦, 好痛心<br />\n但我可以話比自己聽: 好鐘意真正既香港人, 各位真正愛香港既巴絲<br />\n<br />\n但是未得到勝利不容鬆懈<br />\n就算贏一仗我地都要再贏更多<br />\n<br />\n過去幾年輸既野實在太多喇<br />\n淋病,  香港人要用你條命同成個政府僅餘既威信黎賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">616 / 617見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"58ce859d65008991f59fefd345b805d57962557c","tid":1223513,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmlyc6%2Fvideos%2F2413922815343553%2F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8G7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=b0467035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/</a>"},{"pid":"a1f7c169c4fff4fe4ae3cdbee72a66d8c6e0217b","tid":1223513,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded1ed47a7cd88b768ccafcc8e1a1094f2c23216","tid":1223513,"uid":198932,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:21:44.